com.im.njams.sdk

Class Njams

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.im.njams.sdk.Njams
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InstructionListener

    public class Njams
extends Object
implements InstructionListener
    This is an instance of nJAMS. It cares about lifecycle and initializations and holds references to the process models and global variables.
    Author:
    bwand

      • findSerializer

        public <T> Serializer<? super T> findSerializer(Class<T> clazz)
        Gets the serialier with the given class key. If not serializer is registered yet, the superclass hierarchy will be checked recursivly. If neither the class nor any superclass if registered, the interface hierarchy will be checked recursivly. if no (super) interface is registed, null will be returned.
        Type Parameters:
        T - Type of the class
        Parameters:
        clazz - Class for which a serializer will be searched.
        Returns:
        Serizalier of null.
